Brian LautenslagerHeadlineBritish Royal Marines Commandant General Visit and ParadeImage titleFrom left, Sue Smith; Helen Lister; British Royal Marine Attache Col. Al Lister; and Commandant General of the British Royal Marines Maj. Gen. Martin Smith, take a group photo at Col. Lister's house in McLean, Va., prior to attending an Evening Parade at Marine Barracks Washington in Washington, D.C., July 18, 2014. Maj. Gen. Smith is on his first trip to the United States since assuming the role of commandant of the British Royal Marines. (U.S. Marine Corps photo by Staff Sgt.
